{"tid":134791,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"20歲已經好滄桑","createTime":"2017-02-25T17:55:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T06:23:00.000Z","uid":54927,"like":23,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2157d6b0e40aa3cd298fb9ac05ee1bef850848cf","tid":134791,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T17:55:36.000Z","msg":"A0<br />\n中意獨來獨往<br />\n自己旅行 放假周圍走<br />\n有正常社交 有男有女<br />\n對所有野睇到好淡 唔會有咩事令我好緊張<br />\n<br />\n情緒起伏極細  所有事傾向中立，分析。<br />\n無物質追求 呢排賣左 唔用既相機 電話<br />\n狂執屋送賣哂唔用既野<br />\n<br />\n但唔中意同人有太接近既關係<br />\n異性可以話係驚，唔識處理<br />\n普通同女仔傾偈玩都ok<br />\n<br />\n諗野中意諗好遠 所有要做既野都會安排好日子時間計劃<br />\n<br />\n似乎不好也不壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6dd09d684c59ade6f1b5241702a28928867f55","tid":134791,"uid":209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T17:57:40.000Z","msg":"想做到你咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21704f1f5f9913c0d5e7447f8232ba5d7b7071f2","tid":134791,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T18:02:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />毒撚滄咩撚桑<br />\n<br />\n利申 毒撚"},{"pid":"dfd9756e576602f42dfb6f7f126ce7323ecac97c","tid":134791,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T18:04:09.000Z","msg":"對女人冇乜興趣，除非好岩傾，否則一直食草<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"592c412679ddd913e8289995635264bb77143037","tid":134791,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T18:04:13.000Z","msg":"浪子<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"864997e29cf68c55ed55915762a3e829f54c4ecb","tid":134791,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T18:04:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />毒撚滄咩撚桑<br />\n<br />\n利申 毒撚</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc5cbcd83c8386c0b7f2468b3edb3d993a134827","tid":134791,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T18:06:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>浪子<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自己一個時間好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c770e37ff21c49ca3c1effa5f7cff4be5f00cbf","tid":134791,"uid":50162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T18:11:25.000Z","msg":"我都想做到你咁，我對好多野都好緊張，好執著"},{"pid":"992456c487f897da73acebd512dc7ecc1644e69a","tid":134791,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T18:12:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />毒撚滄咩撚桑<br />\n<br />\n利申 毒撚</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a6798c699439fd5f256f42bc4e58a33756de402","tid":134791,"uid":12033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T18:14:59.000Z","msg":"咁先正呀傻鳩 你識唔識架"},{"pid":"2b87d42e085fe004c36a6ea3d7dee133c7a82056","tid":134791,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T18:21:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想做到你咁，我對好多野都好緊張，好執著</blockquote><br />\n細細個係小學放晏 勁緊張自己會遲過人一分鐘食飯果種 好多小事會令我好緊張<br />\n宜家一啲都無"},{"pid":"857dd6ebad6f7a0896baac51d8c7fa640686c934","tid":134791,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T18:22:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁先正呀傻鳩 你識唔識架</blockquote><br />\n但係好似同同年齡既女傾唔埋<br />\n想要一個結衣咁既女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c08e1206f657d981db3a4678aa81df846dd3bae0","tid":134791,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T18:24:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁先正呀傻鳩 你識唔識架</blockquote><br />\n但係好似同同年齡既女傾唔埋<br />\n想要一個結衣咁既女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n訓醒啦，有結衣咁既質素既女仔，唔會對毒撚落咁多心機嫁"},{"pid":"fde708744d1361042912fe6e86677fb49bb31bc5","tid":134791,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T18:37:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>浪子<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自己一個時間好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主係唔係有社交障礙？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5841871bb9079750cf474d98c234764c20ada31f","tid":134791,"uid":70120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T18:37:13.000Z","msg":"我都想學下唔咁易緊張呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我都有同感<br />\n諗多左野就知所有野經歷緊有日都會變過去，自然唔會執著咁多或者強求"},{"pid":"b88d8044126757ac08c249222eb25911bae3c0b0","tid":134791,"uid":17102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T18:44:12.000Z","msg":"正呀<br />\n我都想可以咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"500d840257b44699069d8f15f443d0ab690bc6c6","tid":134791,"uid":84483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T18:46:29.000Z","msg":"同樓豬完全一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前考dse個排係可以咩感覺都無，好輕描淡寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n甚至去到臨放榜個刻同收到成績表個陣都完全無感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去到依家都係咁，咩溝女咩讀書完全無興趣無心情去理，成績得過且過只求過二<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利伸:18歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d6a7e0e19c4c3f728316c29204e4e1444d9d1b6","tid":134791,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T21:51:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />負皮"},{"pid":"6fd986c33c956ac2ce9ec2cbb5ba79c24fe1529f","tid":134791,"uid":29571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T22:25:18.000Z","msg":"同我好似，樓主要唔要出黎做個朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d77f65ffe4ad542ad3b4b0489d532f5d1a475797","tid":134791,"uid":30533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T22:35:42.000Z","msg":"同你差唔多 仲細過你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7267e3d6d9e61d304678272cfea65a78efb519ac","tid":134791,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T23:47:42.000Z","msg":"你呢D叫頂多叫生活平淡, 滄乜撚桑呀你"},{"pid":"f575e58a0b4cc040c076366047ed6ecb474a44d8","tid":134791,"uid":87238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T00:30:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>A0<br />\n中意獨來獨往<br />\n自己旅行 放假周圍走<br />\n有正常社交 有男有女<br />\n對所有野睇到好淡 唔會有咩事令我好緊張<br />\n<br />\n情緒起伏極細  所有事傾向中立，分析。<br />\n無物質追求 呢排賣左 唔用既相機 電話<br />\n狂執屋送賣哂唔用既野<br />\n<br />\n但唔中意同人有太接近既關係<br />\n異性可以話係驚，唔識處理<br />\n普通同女仔傾偈玩都ok<br />\n<br />\n諗野中意諗好遠 所有要做既野都會安排好日子時間計劃<br />\n<br />\n似乎不好也不壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我同你相反，我太情緒化"},{"pid":"4c7fe32dba1d2b92db69f95f16ba5ab80369cfae","tid":134791,"uid":78660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T00:49:15.000Z","msg":"同教主一樣<br />\n已經冇野可以令到我有心跳嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9483f7692c4dbe92e839676debe2d4b1687089f","tid":134791,"uid":78660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T00:49:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同<span style=\"color: red;\">樓</span>主一樣<br />\n已經冇野可以令到我有心跳嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1aa435211b9da8235a3614fe46e3a816389e0b62","tid":134791,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T01:41:41.000Z","msg":"滄桑唔係會得過且過冇計劃架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打發生咩事變到咁?"},{"pid":"62615da456b7d76f14da0b4c0380a557f2074944","tid":134791,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T01:45:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁先正呀傻鳩 你識唔識架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪係 呢啲人不知幾吸引 好似咩事都影響唔到佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得好型棍子 通常諗野會成熟啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a95eed436fbd0466d17c119626002127d3528f67","tid":134791,"uid":22488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T01:46:33.000Z","msg":"「對所有野睇到好淡 唔會有咩事令我好緊張」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實咁樣好正 唔會比任何事影響心情 <br />\n好似以前啲人所謂既君子咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不以物喜 不以己悲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46efce6f4ec5df684f859285d918b7c39fc44384","tid":134791,"uid":737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T01:48:48.000Z","msg":"未去到樓主嘅境界，不過都差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a442c7787fb2c67d74fbde2ae2e2bed8d0c04bb5","tid":134791,"uid":53272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T01:57:47.000Z","msg":"我同樓主一樣<br />\n啲朋友成日話我隱士<br />\n唔知我做緊乜，好似消失左咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本上對好多人同事都提唔起興趣<br />\n唔主動約朋友 翻放工得過且過就過左一日<br />\n唔太鐘意同人有交往 覺得應酬好煩<br />\n同人溝通只做表面個層 唔在意他人眼光<br />\n平淡冷靜理智係好<br />\n不過有時都會幾羨慕有深交既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日諗野都鐘意諗得好遠<br />\n呢個可能係因為獨處既時間太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過自從有左男朋友後<br />\n終於有翻情緒起伏同感興趣既事(姐係佢)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我以前都係好驚同男仔相處(而加都係)<br />\n不過如果想有改變既話<br />\n係需要行前幾步<br />\n但呢啲係迫唔黎既<br />\n可以有翻小小好奇心<br />\n搵下時機到既一刻先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到時就會發現 <br />\n原來對一樣野感興趣<br />\n什至會牽動情緒<br />\n係一件好神奇美妙既事"},{"pid":"9b548492b521bdf1e9e63ea00b53ee68c70a2815","tid":134791,"uid":11447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T02:02:38.000Z","msg":"巴打你應該用瀟灑形容自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7908355ca330271a1e354d29fea9b9ab4719347f","tid":134791,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T02:10:36.000Z","msg":"毒擦就毒擦"},{"pid":"19d95d17a2bfe03c7f8222e9f55728cc2f66ddac","tid":134791,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T02:11:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我同樓主一樣<br />\n啲朋友成日話我隱士<br />\n唔知我做緊乜，好似消失左咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本上對好多人同事都提唔起興趣<br />\n唔主動約朋友 翻放工得過且過就過左一日<br />\n唔太鐘意同人有交往 覺得應酬好煩<br />\n同人溝通只做表面個層 唔在意他人眼光<br />\n平淡冷靜理智係好<br />\n不過有時都會幾羨慕有深交既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日諗野都鐘意諗得好遠<br />\n呢個可能係因為獨處既時間太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過自從有左男朋友後<br />\n終於有翻情緒起伏同感興趣既事(姐係佢)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我以前都係好驚同男仔相處(而加都係)<br />\n不過如果想有改變既話<br />\n係需要行前幾步<br />\n但呢啲係迫唔黎既<br />\n可以有翻小小好奇心<br />\n搵下時機到既一刻先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到時就會發現 <br />\n原來對一樣野感興趣<br />\n什至會牽動情緒<br />\n係一件好神奇美妙既事</blockquote><br />\ngay"},{"pid":"99ddfdc8b14fa70081f9279ee2f1c71d7cd105f6","tid":134791,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T02:13:43.000Z","msg":"有機會就移民 香港男人係全世界最辛苦 最無地企 其他國家女人好尊重男性"},{"pid":"b2cbb18bfc051407ad1e5bcc619d9d02d678d7a7","tid":134791,"uid":43849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T02:40:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我同樓主一樣<br />\n啲朋友成日話我隱士<br />\n唔知我做緊乜，好似消失左咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本上對好多人同事都提唔起興趣<br />\n唔主動約朋友 翻放工得過且過